.jpg|80px|alt=Ground-level view of two curved buildings that slightly resemble sails; the sun is setting in the distance.]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 245\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 804\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 70\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2008\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{coord|1|16|51.97|N|103|51|10.06|E}}\n| 215th-tallest building in the world and tallest residential skyscraper in Singapore; also known as the Marina Bay Tower<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emporis.com/application/?nav=building&lng=3&id=marinabaytower-singapore-singapore|title=Marina Bay Tower|publisher=Emporis.com|accessdate=16 July 2009}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | publisher = SkyscraperPage.com | title = The Sail @ Marina Bay | url = http://skyscraperpage.com/cities/?buildingID=27842 | accessdate = 2 February 2008 }}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |8=\n| <span style=\"display:none\">36.0</span>[[Marina Bay Financial Centre|Marina Bay Financial Centre Tower 3]]\n|[[File:Marina Bay Financial Centre.JPG|80px]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 245\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 804\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 45\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2012\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{coord|1|16|48.13|N|103|51|15.08|E}}\n|<ref>{{cite web | publisher = SkyscraperPage.com | title = Marina Bay Financial Centre Office Tower \"1\" | url = http://skyscraperpage.com/cities/?buildingID=55959 | accessdate = 16 July 2009 }}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |8=\n| <span style=\"display:none\">36.0</span>[[Ocean Financial Centre]]\n|[[File:Ocean Financial Centre artist impression.jpg|80px|alt=Artist's image of a complete skyscraper; the building is portrayed with a slightly curved glass facade with an angled roofline.]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 245\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 804\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 43\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2011\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{coord|1|16|59.52|N|103|51|10.77|E}}\n|<ref 