ne Raffles Quay South Tower]]\n| [[File:One Raffles Quay 4.JPG|80px|alt=Ground-level view of two square buildings with identical all-glass facades]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 140\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 459\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 29\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2006\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | {{coord|1|16|53.04|N|103|51|6.52|E}}\n|<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Emporis.com | title = One Raffles Quay South Tower | url = http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/bu/?id=1rafflesquaysouthtower-singapore-singapore | accessdate = 26 January 2008 }}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Tallest under construction==\nThis lists buildings that are [[Construction|under construction]] in [[Singapore]]. A floor count of 40&nbsp;stories is used as the cutoff for buildings whose heights have not yet been released by their developers.\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Name||class=\"unsortable\"|Image||Height (m)*||Height (ft)*||Floors||Year<br /><small>(est.)</small>|| Coordinates||class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| <span style=\"display:none\">08.0</span>CapitaSpring\n| \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 280\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 920\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 51\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/business/182b-tower-to-replace-golden-shoe-car-park|title=S$1.82b tower to replace Golden Shoe Carpark|publisher=The Straits Times|access-date=2017-07-15|language=en-SG}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.tnp.sg/news/business/tower-going-old-golden-shoe-car-park-named-capitaspring|title=Tower going up at old Golden Shoe Car Park named CapitaSpring|publisher=The New Paper|access-date=2018-04-13|language=en-SG}}</ref>\n|-\n| <span style=\"display:none\">08.0</span>Avenue South Residence\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|250\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|820\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|56\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2023\n| style=\"text